works.description: Here comes an amazing deal for those who intend to have a one-of-a-kind vacation or need to impress their clients or near and dear ones. For a mere $70,000 a night, you can rent the entire country of Liechtenstein. The Principality of Liechtenstein is a tiny landlocked alpine country in Central Europe, bordered by Switzerland to the west and south and by Austria to the east. Its area is just about 61.7 square miles, and it has an estimated population of 35,000. For the price, you can enjoy the beautiful Alps, lush valleys and the amazing castles of Liechtenstein.
